arStrings.szText: "Do you know anything about this Thieves Guild emblem?"
You goddamn bastard! Get that filthy shite out of here before I melt down that medallion and--
Oh, my goodness. I didn't know that was still in me, I-- my apologies. Truly, apologies, I-- you didn't know. Of course you didn't know. Umm, the Thieves Guild and I do not have a friendly past.
That emblem is a reminder of my every failure in life. A reminder that my children will make the same damned mistakes I did, and I can't stop them.
